  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800600/extras/7ba414f1d0a8d5634c44ef879051c242.poster.avif?t=1636776457\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800600/extras/7ba414f1d0a8d5634c44ef879051c242.webm?t=1636776457\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800600/extras/7ba414f1d0a8d5634c44ef879051c242.mp4?t=1636776457\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Had a rough day you want to relieve? Or do you just want to have some violent fun? You can in this little arcade game. <br><br>+ PUNCH, PULL, TWIST to earn points and unlock all 3 stages. <br>+ Go crazy in \"Freemode\" unleashing max damage on your foes as they make funny noises.<br>+ 6 intense beats to go along with your intense beatings.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800600/extras/87f9909bc2eeecd28bbb216dbdfcfcc3.poster.avif?t=1636776457\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800600/extras/87f9909bc2eeecd28bbb216dbdfcfcc3.webm?t=1636776457\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800600/extras/87f9909bc2eeecd28bbb216dbdfcfcc3.mp4?t=1636776457\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
